flowchart TD
    A[Event in Claude's cycle] --> B{Hook configured?}
    B -->|No| C[Proceed normally]
    B -->|Yes| D[Execute hook command]
    D --> E[Hook receives JSON via stdin]
    E --> F[Hook processes and decides]
    F --> G{Exit code?}
    G -->|0| H[Success: process output]
    G -->|2| I[Block: show error]
    G -->|Other| J[Non-blocking error]
    H --> K{JSON output?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Apply decisions]
    K -->|No| M[Add stdout to context]
    L --> C
    M --> C
    I --> N[Operation blocked]
    J --> C
